className.description: Sets the style name of the icon

:rotate.description_zh: 图标旋转角度（IE9 无效）

spin.description: Whether there is a rotation animation

:style.description: Style the icon, such as fontSize and color
:style.description_zh: 设置图标的样式，例如 fontSize 和 color

twoToneColor.description: Only two-color icons apply. Sets the main color of the two-color icon
twoToneColor.description_zh: 仅适用双色图标。设置双色图标的主要颜色

component.description: Controls how icons are rendered, typically a <svg> React component with a render root tag
component.description_zh: 控制如何渲染图标，通常是一个渲染根标签为 <svg> 的 React 组件

fill.description: The color of the svg element fill
